a good educational app.

00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:55.180
And then you'll be able to get
this very powerful distribution

00:13:55.180 --> 00:13:59.220
channel and sell
your apps or just

00:13:59.220 --> 00:14:02.800
give it for free
to many schools.

00:14:02.800 --> 00:14:06.580
You can go to this URL--
developers.google.com/edu--

00:14:06.580 --> 00:14:09.190
and there is a sign-up form
where you can sign up to get

00:14:09.190 --> 00:14:12.130
notified when this opt-in
opens for everybody.

00:14:16.760 --> 00:14:21.200
So just to summarize the tips
that I've already mentioned,

00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:24.710
any high-quality promotional
images is a good thing.

00:14:24.710 --> 00:14:28.940
Having good screenshots and
detailed descriptions is also

00:14:28.940 --> 00:14:32.590
valuable, helps users
to make their decision.

00:14:32.590 --> 00:14:35.340
It's important to
monitor the email address

00:14:35.340 --> 00:14:36.940
that you use to
publish your apps,

00:14:36.940 --> 00:14:39.980
because Google will use it
in case something is wrong.

00:14:39.980 --> 00:14:41.930
It's good to monitor
the user feedback,

00:14:41.930 --> 00:14:44.780
and there are tools
for that in Web Store.

00:14:44.780 --> 00:14:47.000
It's also good to localize
to multiple languages

00:14:47.000 --> 00:14:50.500
if you target users in
other languages as well.

00:14:50.500 --> 00:14:52.120
And invest into
your own marketing,

00:14:52.120 --> 00:14:54.930
and then if you have a
good app, then chances

00:14:54.930 --> 00:14:57.670
will be higher that Google
Merchandising team will

00:14:57.670 --> 00:15:01.980
notice your app and make
it even more popular.

