So the built-in
statistics is something

00:15:13.510 --> 00:15:16.430
that you just have for free
for every Web Store item.

00:15:16.430 --> 00:15:19.210
currently, it includes
impressions and installs

00:15:19.210 --> 00:15:21.220
that you get on a daily basis.

00:15:21.220 --> 00:15:24.490
