soon sales statistics,

00:15:24.490 --> 00:15:28.720
so if your app uses any of
Web Store's payment options,

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:31.510
you will see additional
charts and tables

00:15:31.510 --> 00:15:34.580
summarizing how much
money you're making.

00:15:34.580 --> 00:15:36.730
And the last option
that you can use

00:15:36.730 --> 00:15:40.690
is you can just give us
your Google Analytics ID,

00:15:40.690 --> 00:15:43.460
